rvices designed to nurture your mind, body, and spirit. Visit us today and begin your journey towards a healthier, more balanced life!","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"efe33974-5b7f-4450-bfef-3529d98a6eca","name":"The Lotus Center","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/a77e3c_4367da46d615469e8b9ecf805ffe1d62%7Emv2.jpg/v1/fit/w_2500,h_1330,al_c/a77e3c_4367da46d615469e8b9ecf805ffe1d62%7Emv2.jpg","modality":"Massage, Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing","modalities":["Massage","Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.63214,"lng":-155.990229,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Experience famous Kona massage & Kona spa services at The Lotus Center in Royal Kona Resort. Lomi lomi, deep tissue, facials & more. Book your escape today!","centerType":"spa","centerTypeLabel":"Spa","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true}],"totalPractitioners":10,"totalCenters":10,"citiesServed":["Captain Cook","Hilo","Holualoa","Kailua-Kona","Kealakekua","Kohala Coast","Pahoa","Volcano"]}]
